# Mini App Frontend

## Structure

- `src/game/` ‚Äî engine, constants, audio (no DOM)
- `src/lib/telegram.ts` ‚Äî WebApp SDK wrapper; `getStartParam()` for challenge links
- `src/lib/api.ts` ‚Äî fetch calls to Railway API; caches `session_token`; `prepareShare()` for `/share/prepare`
- `src/lib/revive.ts` ‚Äî AdsGram rewarded revive gate (optional monetization)
- `src/lib/adsgram.ts` ‚Äî AdsGram SDK + `showRewardAd()`
- `src/lib/pending-submit.ts` ‚Äî score defer on pagehide when revive offered
- `src/lib/analytics.ts` ‚Äî TON Builders funnel events (share, revive, tutorial)
- `src/lib/telegram-analytics.ts` ‚Äî SDK init; `appName` must be `corporate_ladder`
- `src/lib/avatar.ts`, `hr-memo.ts`, `capture-mode.ts` ‚Äî home avatar, in-run memos, OG capture
- `src/lib/branding.ts` ‚Äî Prompt Anatomy co-branding (`VITE_PROMPT_ANATOMY_URL`)
- `src/lib/effects.ts` ‚Äî visual effects (reduced-motion aware)
- `src/app.ts` ‚Äî UI controller and DOM wiring
- `src/template.ts` ‚Äî HTML shell
- `src/style.css` ‚Äî design tokens and utilities

## Rules

- Never embed `TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN` or Supabase keys in client code.
- Use `getInitData()` for `/auth/me`, `/runs`, and `/share/prepare`; use cached `session_token` for `POST /leaderboard/me`.
- Leaderboard tabs: Daily and Weekly only (v1).
- Share: `POST /share/prepare` then `WebApp.shareMessage(preparedMessageId)`; clipboard fallback on failure.
- Styling: Tailwind utility classes via Vite plugin; no CDN Tailwind in production.
- Game logic changes must match [ROADMAP.md](../../ROADMAP.md) ¬ß Shipped baseline; new features need [mvp-scope](../../docs/mvp-scope.md) boundary check.

## Shipped mechanics guardrails (v1.6+)

See [ROADMAP.md](../../ROADMAP.md) ¬ß Shipped baseline (v1.5 ‚Üí v2.2.0 + `[Unreleased]`). Do not regress without spec update:

- Rank-gated obstacles: Meeting (Intern) ‚Üí Reorg (Manager+) ‚Üí Deadline (`burnout` type, **Director+** 20y) ‚Üí **Gate** (Manager+) ‚Üí **Plant** (**CEO+** only)
- **Director @ 20y (v2.1.0):** Intern ‚Üí Manager @ 10y ‚Üí Director @ 20y ‚Üí CEO @ 35y
- **Adaptive rookie ramp (v2.1.0):** 20 rungs / 0.30 spawn cap until Manager for low career-best players
- **Challenge param (v2.1.0):** `startapp=c_*` via `getStartParam()`; beat-your-gap in `corp_ladder_last_run` localStorage
- **Three-lane corridor (v1.8.5):** center aisle visual only ‚Äî TAP LEFT/RIGHT unchanged; no center tap
- **Scripted tutorial (v1.8.5):** first 3 imminent rungs ‚Äî clear ‚Üí meeting RIGHT ‚Üí coffee LEFT
- Intern tutorial ramp: lower spawn rate first 12 rungs; forced coffee inject on `rungs[2]` by rung 8 if none collected (v1.8.4)
- Reorg fairness: next rung (`rungs[1]`) exempt from swap during reorg ticks; imminent reorg shows **Frozen** badge (v1.8.4)
- Tap rate limit (v1.8.4): `MIN_TAP_INTERVAL_MS` 120ms
- Promotion spawn sync (v1.8.4): `checkPromotions()` before `generateRung()`
- 2s energy drain pause on promotion
- HUD milestone chip; game-over death cause + retry tips
- **Score trust:** career high updates only after successful submit ‚Äî [`lib/score-trust.ts`](../../apps/mini-app/src/lib/score-trust.ts)
- Code type `burnout` vs UI label **Deadline** ‚Äî see [docs/mvp-scope.md](../../docs/mvp-scope.md) terminology table

Do not add Legends tab or new control schemes without scope approval.

## Shipped UI guardrails (v1.8.2 ‚Üí v1.8.5)

- Bottom **tap deck** (`#tapControlsBar`) ‚Äî visible h-28 buttons; no full-play-area transparent overlay
- **Deck-first** onboarding: `#hudTapHint` + `.tap-deck-hint` (not tap-prompt bar)
- **`#gameContentColumn` (v1.8.3+)** ‚Äî single gutter wraps HUD + play + tap deck
- `#ladderTrack` width from layout ‚Äî player position from DOM, not fixed 192px
- In-run copy via **HR memo rail** ‚Äî avoid shell toasts over tap deck during play
- **`#imminentHint` (v1.9)** ‚Äî next-rung guidance through Intern phase (**40 rungs**, `INTERN_HINT_RUNGS` in `lib/debug.ts`); tap-deck-hint pulse first 5 taps only
- **Corridor visuals (v1.8.5):** `.rung-center--corridor`, `.player-at-corridor`
- Layout CI: `npm run qa:layout` ‚Äî play width stable after first tap

UI patterns: [DESIGN_SYSTEM.md](../../DESIGN_SYSTEM.md). Release Status: [ROADMAP.md](../../ROADMAP.md).

## Platform + analytics (v2.1+)

- TON Builders init before first render ‚Äî [telegram-analytics.ts](../../apps/mini-app/src/lib/telegram-analytics.ts); `appName` must be **`corporate_ladder`** (case-sensitive)
- Funnel events via [analytics.ts](../../apps/mini-app/src/lib/analytics.ts) ‚Äî `tutorial_complete`, `share_tap`, `share_success`, `revive_offer`, `revive_complete`; not v1.1 analytics dashboard
- Analytics init failure must not block app mount (guard in bootstrap)
- Score defer on pagehide when revive offered ‚Äî [pending-submit.ts](../../apps/mini-app/src/lib/pending-submit.ts)
- Daily leaderboard fetch after score submit completes (not in parallel with submit)

## Local Dev

